hub.name: Portfolio
hub.cardDescription: For the biggest impact, you can support all our projects around the world. The money will be split between the portfolio so that our movement can flourish in all parts of the world.

impactReportParagraphs.paragraph: Our Collection Hubs in India, Indonesia, and Cambodia all intercept waste before it even reaches the environment by collecting it directly from households as well as waterways, and fishermen's bycatch from the ocean. We help build these collection systems, providing communities with access to waste management for the first time to prevent open dumping and burning. Every financial contribution helps to expand the model across coastal regions in this world and creates stable and dignified jobs for local communities.

Unsere Collection Hubs in Indien, Indonesien und Kambodscha fangen den Abfall ab, bevor er überhaupt in die Umwelt gelangt, indem sie ihn direkt von Haushalten, Flüssen und als Beifang der Fischer im Meer einsammeln. Wir helfen beim Aufbau dieser Sammelsysteme, die den Gemeinden zum ersten Mal Zugang zur Abfallwirtschaft verschaffen, um wildes Zugemülle in der Umwelt und offene Verbrennung zu verhindern. Jeder finanzielle Beitrag trägt dazu bei, das Modell auf die Küstenregionen dieser Welt auszuweiten, und schafft stabile und würdige Arbeitsplätze für die lokalen Gemeinschaften.

After the waste has been collected, it is sorted into different categories so each material can be disposed of correctly. Recyclable plastic is sold to local recyclers, non-recyclable plastic is processed in the most environmentally sustainable way available. We track all the plastic recovered through the CleanHub app.

Nach dem Sammeln der Abfälle werden diese in verschiedene Kategorien eingeteilt, damit jedes Material korrekt entsorgt werden kann. Recycelbare Kunststoffe werden an örtliche Recycler verkauft, nicht recycelbare Kunststoffe werden auf die ökologisch nachhaltigste Weise verarbeitet. Wir verfolgen das gesamte zurückgewonnene Plastik über die CleanHub-App.

childrenHubs.name: Green Worm Sorting
childrenHubs.cardDescription: Greens Worms Waste Management organizes door-to-door collection services across southern India, with the help of women empowerment groups.

childrenHubs.name: Recity-MRF-Pondicherry
childrenHubs.cardDescription: Founded to keep plastics out of the environment, Recity are creating a circular economy - enabling value chain collaborations between brands and consumers

childrenHubs.name: Vrecycle_MRF
childrenHubs.cardDescription: vRecycle helps over 25K homes manage their waste self-sufficiently and have built more than 2K composters and 200 community recycling points.

childrenHubs.name: EcoBali Collection
childrenHubs.cardDescription: ecoBali was founded on the idea of 'getting responsible with waste' due to the lack of waste management in Bali and are working to a more circular approach to waste.

childrenHubs.name: Comped Phnom Penh
childrenHubs.cardDescription: COMPED is on a mission to collect plastic waste along river and water canals to protect biological diversity in Cambodia

childrenHubs.name: Got Bag Warehouse
childrenHubs.cardDescription: GOT BAG developed the world’s first backpack made of Ocean Impact Plastic. They collect plastic waste as bycatch with a network of fishermen and set up waste management structures in coastal areas to prevent plastic waste ending up in the ocean.

statement: For every sales call booked and attended, we commit to collect 5kg of plastic waste.
customerImpactGoalTitle: Ocean bound plastic recovered thanks to CleanHub Bookings
impactReportHeader: CleanHub Bookings protects our oceans from plastic waste
impactPlasticCollectionDescription:
Two billion people in coastal regions don’t have access to proper waste management. Trash is either openly burned, dumped, or piled onto poorly managed landfills, destined to impact our climate.

Waste management systems prevent trash from ever leaking into nature or being burnt under the open sky.
